<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184167>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Altimyia boliviana, gen. & sp. nov. 1. Head of male, lateral view. 2. Hind tibia, anterior view. 3. Sternite 5. 4. Cercal plate and surstyli, dorsal view. 5. Cercal plate and surstylus, lateral view. 6. Phallic complex, lateral view. 7. Ovipositor, dorsal view. 8. Ovipositor, ventral view and spermathecae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184167/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

